      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·004.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">揚之水.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>揚之水，不流束楚，終鮮兄弟，維予與女，無信人之言，人實迋女。
揚之水，不流束薪，終鮮兄弟，維予二人，無信人之言，人實不信！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The torrent carries bundles of briers;
That person will not collect me.
He will not collect me,
And I languish, and am grieved.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-004__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
