      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·004.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">揚之水.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>揚之水，白石鑿鑿，素衣朱襮，從子于沃，既見君子，云何不樂。
揚之水，白石皓皓，素衣朱繡，從子于鵠，既見君子，云何其憂。
揚之水，白石粼粼，我聞有命，不敢以告人！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The torrent carries bundles of faggots;
That person will not comfort me.
He will not comfort me,
And I languish, and am grieved.</seg>
      </tuv>
